(34, '2,4,6,7', 'Alinea.ID', 'Alinea.ID', '<p>Nama Klien:&nbsp;<strong>alinea.id</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Website:&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://www.alinea.id/\">https://www.alinea.id/</a>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pekerjaan:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Website &amp; Mobile Development</li>\r\n	<li>Mainten Web Server</li>\r\n	<li>SEO</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Alinea adalah situs berita digital, untuk pengguna internet cerdas. Kami memberi konteks kepada berita dan informasi melalui format kreatif dan mudah diakses pengguna melalui perangkat yang selalu mereka bawa: ponsel dan tablet.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Alinea tampil dengan mengusung semangat zaman ketika ia dilahirkan: transformasi digital dan media sosial yang sudah jadi bagian hidup miliaran orang sehari-hari.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Liputan kami mencakup tiga hal esensial yang penting bagi semua orang, yaitu fakta, data, dan kata. Kami meyakini, pertalian ketiga hal tersebut akan menghasilkan wawasan yang berharga bagi semua pembaca, dan juga penting saat mereka mengambil keputusan.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pendiri Alinea terdiri-dari anak-anak muda yang pernah bekerja di media berstandar tinggi. Kami juga memiliki jaringan kontributor dan koresponden yang tersebar dari Timur sampai Barat Indonesia.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kami sadar, perkembangan teknologi akan menentukan masa depan situs berita digital. Karena itu, jurnalis dan engineer kami duduk di ruang redaksi yang sama untuk saling bahu membahu bereksperimen mengenai hal-hal baru. Engineer juga menyatu dengan redaksi untuk mengembangkan, mengolah, dan menyajikan konten yang kami sarikan dari Big Data dan Artificial Intelligence.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kami selalu terbuka terhadap gagasan dan hal baru. Anda bisa menghubungi kami melalui email, Twitter, dan Facebook.</p>', '<p>Client Name:&nbsp;<strong>alinea.id&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Website:&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://www.alinea.id/\">https://www.alinea.id/</a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Works:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Website &amp; Mobile Development</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Maintenance Web Server</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>SEO</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Alinea is a digital news site, for smart internet users. We provide context to news and information through creative formats and are easily accessible to users through the devices they always carry: cellphones and tablets.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Paragraph appears with the spirit of the era when he was born: digital transformation and social media that have become part of the lives of billions of people everyday.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our coverage covers three essential things that are important to everyone, namely facts, data and words. We believe that these three links will produce valuable insights for all readers, and are also important when making decisions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The founder of Alinea consists of young people who have worked in high standard media. We also have a network of contributors and correspondents spread from East to West Indonesia.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are aware that technological developments will determine the future of digital news sites. Therefore, our journalists and engineers sit in the same newsroom to work together to experiment with new things. Engineers also unite with editors to develop, process and present content that we extract from Big Data and Artificial Intelligence.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are always open to new ideas and things. You can contact us via email, Twitter and Facebook.</p>', '748alineasosmed1.png', '2020-01-13 07:43:22', '2020-01-31 09:54:34', 0, 1, 20),
(35, '2,4,6,7', 'Tek.ID', 'Tek.ID', '<p>Nama Klien: <strong>Tek.ID</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Website:&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://www.tek.id/\">https://www.tek.id/</a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pekerjaan:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Website &amp; Mobile Development</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Maintenance Web Server</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>SEO</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Tek.id adalah portal berita teknologi. Kami membahas consumer tech, gaya hidup digital, inovasi, terobosan sains, masa depan, dan analisis bermakna bagi pembaca.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tim editorial Tek.id berasal dari latar belakang yang beragam. Kami menerapkan jurnalisme sudut pandang orang pertama untuk konten review. Dengan demikian, jurnalis bisa memberikan pandangan berbeda atas fakta yang sama, sesuai kepribadian mereka, dan pembaca bisa membuat kesimpulan sendiri.</p>', '<p>Client Name: <strong>Tek.ID</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Website:&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://www.tek.id/\">https://www.tek.id/</a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Works:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Website &amp; Mobile Development</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Maintenance Web Server</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>SEO</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Tek.id is a technology news portal. We discuss consumer tech, digital lifestyle, innovation, scientific breakthroughs, the future, and meaningful analysis for readers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Tek.id editorial team comes from diverse backgrounds. We apply journalism from a first-person perspective to review content. Thus, journalists can give different views on the same facts, according to their personalities, and readers can make their own conclusions.</p>', '4280teklogo.png', '2020-01-13 07:56:55', '2020-01-13 10:05:15', 0, 1, 21),
(36, '6,7', 'Posjateng.ID', 'Posjateng.ID', '<p>Nama Klien: <strong>Posjateng.ID</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Website:&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://www.posjateng.id/\">https://www.posjateng.id/</a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Posjateng.id adalah portal berita gayeng. Sejalan dengan jargon Jawa Tengah yang penuh semangat, berani, tangguh, jujur, ramah, menggembirakan, harmonis, dan hangat.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kami berharap bisa menjadi jawaban dari berseliwerannya berita bohong (hoax), informasi yang sepenggal-sepenggal, maupun kabar tanpa konfirmasi namun sudah dianggap sebagai kebenaran. Terutama di wilayah kami, Jawa Tengah dan Daerah Istimewa Yogyakarta.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Didominasi anak-anak muda yang berpengalaman di dunia jurnalistik, Posjateng.id tak sekadar meramaikan industri media tapi kami membawa kebaruan.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bukan hanya memberitakan isu-isu nasional, kami juga konsern dengan peristiwa di sekitar kita yang disampaikan secara faktual, tajam, dan kontekstual. Sisi lain yang sering kali dilupakan wartawan juga menjadi fokus kami.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Berita kami mencakup tiga hal esensial yaitu fakta, data, dan kata. Kami berharap pertalian ketiganya akan menghasilkan wawasan berharga bagi semua pembaca.</p>', '<p>Client Name: <strong>Posjateng.ID</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Website:&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://www.posjateng.id/\">https://www.posjateng.id/</a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Posjateng.id is a gay news portal. In line with Central Java jargon which is full of enthusiasm, brave, tough, honest, friendly, uplifting, harmonious, and warm.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We hope to be an answer to the hoaxing of hoaxes, piece of information, and news without confirmation but which are considered as truth. Especially in our region, Central Java and Yogyakarta Special Region.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dominated by young people who are experienced in the world of journalism, Posjateng.id not only enlivens the media industry but we bring novelty.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Not only reporting on national issues, we are also concerned about the events around us that are conveyed factually, sharply, and contextually. The other side that journalists often forget is also our focus.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our news covers three essential things namely facts, data and words. We hope that these three links will produce valuable insights for all readers.</p>', '3996posjateng.png', '2020-01-13 09:41:12', '2020-09-18 04:19:05', 0, 1, 22),
(37, '6,7', 'Jatimpos.ID', 'Jatimpos.ID', '<p>Nama Klien: <strong>Jatimpos.ID</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Website:&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://www.jatimpos.id/\">https://www.jatimpos.id/</a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Cita-cita membangun Indonesia dari pinggiran hanya utopis bila saluran informasi sekadar masif di Ibu kota. Publik butuh banyak lubang informasi baru yang bernas, akurat dan terpercaya. Hal inilah salah satu yang melatari lahirnya Jatimpos.id.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hadir di tengah limpahan informasi lokal maupun nasional, Jatimpos.id diharapkan menjadi bagian dari pilar demokrasi, sebagai alat kontrol kebijakan pemerintah daerah dan perilaku publik, sekaligus menjadi sarana pemberdayaan masyarakat, khususnya di Jawa Timur.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tak mudah bagi kami berdiri kokoh di tengah derasnya arus informasi, serta meredupnya batas fakta dan hoaks yang justru mendorong apatisme publik terhadap karya jurnalistik. Karena itulah, kami berpegang pada dua prinsip penting yakni: Faktual dan Imparsial.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Faktual sebagai upaya mencari kebenaran dengan berpijak pada kelengkapan, keakuratan, dan kecermatan dan Imparsial, mengacu pada laku jurnalistik yang menjunjung tinggi nilai keseimbangan (balance, non-partisanship, neutral).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dengan dua prinsip itu, Jatimpos.id berharap bisa berlayar mengarungi dinamika sosial, budaya, ekonomi, dan politik untuk memberikan yang terbaik untuk publik Jawa Timur.</p>', '<p>Client Name: <strong>Jatimpos.ID</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Website:&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://www.jatimpos.id/\">https://www.jatimpos.id/</a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The goal of building Indonesia from the periphery is only utopian if the information channel is merely massive in the capital. The public needs many new holes of information that are pithy, accurate and reliable. This is one of the reasons for the birth of Jatimpos.id.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Present in the midst of an abundance of local and national information, Jatimpos.id is expected to be part of the pillars of democracy, as a means of controlling local government policies and public behavior, as well as a means of community empowerment, especially in East Java.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is not easy for us to stand firm amid the swift flow of information, as well as the dimming of the boundaries of facts and hoaxes which actually encourages public apathy towards journalistic work. For this reason, we stick to two important principles, namely: Factual and Impartial.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Factual as an effort to find the truth by standing on completeness, accuracy, and accuracy and Imparsial, refers to journalistic behavior that upholds the value of balance (balance, non-partisanship, neutral).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With these two principles, Jatimpos.id hopes to sail across the social, cultural, economic, and political dynamics to provide the best for the public of East Java.</p>', '1284jatimpos.png', '2020-01-13 09:44:19', '2020-01-13 09:44:19', 0, 1, 23),
(38, '6,7', 'Jurnaljabar.ID', 'Jurnaljabar.ID', '<p>Nama Klien: <strong>Jurnaljabar.ID</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Website:<strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.jurnaljabar.id/\">https://www.jurnaljabar.id/</a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jawa Barat begitu istimewa bagi kami. Bukan hanya sebagai provinsi terbesar di Tanah Air, tetapi rumah bagi keluhungan nilai spiritual, kearifan lokal dan budaya. Meski Jawa Barat juga bukan tanpa cela. Wilayah ini disebut menempati urutan tertinggi penyebaran hoax di Indonesia.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Berlatar itulah kami melahirkan Jurnaljabar.id. Media khas Jawa Barat yang diharapkan menjadi jawaban dari semakin tipisnya sekat antara fakta dan fiksi, serta kian sulitnya membedakan mana informasi dan mana imajinasi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jurnaljabar.id akan berupaya mengedepankan akurasi dan verifikasi dalam setiap berita yang diproduksi, di samping tentu saja menjunjung tinggi kode etik dan mengamalkan rumus-rumus dasar jurnalistik.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kami juga mengutamakan keamanan (security) atas dampak yang ditimbulkan dari berita-berita yang kami tayangkaan, serta kebenaran (true) dari berita-berita yang kami sajikan.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Visi kami, menjadi media andal dan mata rantai industri media digital di Jawa Barat. Kami optimistis dapat memberi warna dan menjadi salah satu pilihan terbaik bagi pembaca dan stakeholder, khususnya di Bumi Pasundan.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dukungan pembaca dan stakeholder berupa kesempatan, kerja sama, kritik, dan saran menjadi bagian penting untuk berkembang dan mewujudkan visi kami dan Jurnaljabar.id bisa menjadi saluran informasi akurat, berimbang, kontekstual dan terpercaya.</p>', '<p>Client Name: <strong>Jurnaljabar.ID</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Website:<strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.jurnaljabar.id/\">https://www.jurnaljabar.id/</a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>West Java is so special to us. Not only as the largest province in the country, but home to the spiritual values, local wisdom and culture. Although West Java is also not flawless. This region is said to occupy the highest rank of hoax distribution in Indonesia.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It was against this background that we gave birth to Jurnaljabar.id. West Java&#39;s distinctive media is expected to be the answer to the increasingly thin barrier between fact and fiction, and the more difficult it is to distinguish between information and imagination.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jurnaljabar.id will strive to prioritize accuracy and verification in every news produced, in addition to of course upholding the code of ethics and applying basic journalistic formulas.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We also prioritize security (security) for the impact caused by the news that we report, as well as the truth (true) of the news that we present.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our vision is to become a reliable media and digital media industry chain in West Java. We are optimistic that we can give color and become one of the best choices for readers and stakeholders, especially in Pasundan Earth.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The support of readers and stakeholders in the form of opportunities, cooperation, criticism, and suggestions becomes an important part of developing and realizing our vision and Jurnaljabar.id can be an accurate, balanced, contextual and trusted information channel.</p>', '1704jurnaljabar.png', '2020-01-13 09:54:56', '2020-01-13 09:54:56', 0, 1, 24),
